pid":"4960137987efc03d0721dadf2320dc1a22e3c925","tid":494378,"uid":58670,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:33:57.000Z","msg":"樓上有人講點解唔餵野食，可以參考攝影師的說法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nVideo shows the polar bear clinging to life, its white hair limply covering its thin, bony frame. One of the bear's back legs drags behind it as it walks, likely due to muscle atrophy. Looking for food, the polar bear slowly rummages through a nearby trashcan used seasonally by Inuit fishers. It finds nothing and resignedly collapses back down onto the ground.<br />\n<br />\nIn the days since Nicklen posted the footage, he's been asked why he didn&rsquo;t intervene.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Of course, that crossed my mind,&quot; said Nicklen. &quot;But it's not like I walk around with a tranquilizer gun or 400 pounds of seal meat.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nAnd even if he did, said Nicklen, he only would have been prolonging the bear's misery. Plus, feeding wild polar bears is illegal in Canada.<br />\n<br />\nThe wildlife photographer says he filmed the bear's slow, beleaguered death because he didn't want it to die in vain.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.nationalgeographic.com/2017/12/polar-bear-starving-arctic-sea-ice-melt-climate-change-spd/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.nationalgeographic.com%2F2017%2F12%2Fpolar-bear-starving-arctic-sea-ice-melt-climate-change-spd%2F&d=I9q57khBnM14iE4uKaveFosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=54f46fe3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.nationalgeographic.com/2017/12/polar-bear-starving-arctic-sea-ice-melt-climate-change-spd/</a>"},{"pid":"cadce1633747c5ab0b955b712768a6482e7ae3a6","tid":494378,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:39:38.000Z","msg":"人類正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當初恐龍又係咁絕左種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75703ee97d973f3679bdb309c9d4a350844fcc3e","tid":494378,"uid":8000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:50:21.000Z","msg":"講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫馬會同商場閂細d個冷氣先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b4655010cc0ca4d6c3bfd020019fd7e5f97092","tid":494378,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:51:27.000Z","msg":"好似香港d廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8704ebdf777232d7dc06ea471ccdca1d9d256083","tid":494378,"uid":13752,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:51:33.000Z","msg":"連登只係一班5p小學雞集合之地<br />\n連登仔啲觀念根本就係錯撚哂 已經唔關假膠事<br />\n只希望大家講出黎嘅嘢唔會影響到心智未成熟嘅後生仔"},{"pid":"e8aed942bc6284211e96ebec5596608ea203aef6","tid":494378,"uid":188,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:51:41.000Z","msg":"環境係呃窮人守規<br />\n<br />\n你呢個係窮人 你世世代代都係服侍有錢人下一代<br />\n你就算中六合彩想上遊小小 都係服侍有錢人<br />\n<br />\n有錢佬最想就係你班賤民 安安份份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你下一代 服侍佢下一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講咩打杖會洗牌 我肯定佢安全過你 第一時間走先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b076c2c51dc6ce4aa08e50f15932ff0d3a44047a","tid":494378,"uid":90820,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:54:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔幫又要影人<br />\n拍野浪費資源又唔環保<br />\n<br />\n佢咁瘦又唔幫人渡過難關<br />\n環保撚真係黑心，得個講字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以點解話班偽善撚咁撚偽善, 永遠只係識做旁觀者, 完全唔諗住幫手, 只係識嘴炮</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>SeaLegacy聯合創始人兼攝影師 Paul Nicklen 在接受《國家地理雜誌》採訪時說，即使有足夠的食物餵養動物，它不僅是危險的，而且在野外接近北極熊也是非法的。Cristina Mittermeier 認為，該熊只剩下幾天的生命，任何行動都會延長其痛苦。</blockquote><br />\n到底你哋呢班文盲有無睇內文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且拍攝生態片/相<br />\n係唔可以介入<br />\n因為會影響到自然生態<br />\n常識嚟㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa1aa55eed52c12733f0bf3c44e7526352728f6","tid":494378,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:00:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記得之前炒過車喎<br />\n有隻北極熊餓死左，D人響度話氣候暖化，點知影相嗰個話隻熊老得滯，自己捕食唔到先死</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n儘管氣候變化有可能是導致熊出現病態的原因，但有人警告說，根據一段短片得出結論可能為時過早。Cristina Mittermeier 承認：「不可能說出牠為什麼處於這種狀態，也許可能是因為受傷或疾病。」 但她指，人為造成的氣候變化導致了熊的挨餓。<br />\n<br />\n但艾伯塔大學的 Ian Stirling 對英國 Metro News 表示，這隻熊<span style=\"color: red;\">可能</span>是生病，又或者是年老。<br />\n<br />\nCristina Mittermeier 說，<span style=\"color: red;\">這隻熊沒有明顯的受傷，年紀也太年輕了。她認為這是無關緊要的，「重要的是它正在挨餓，而且當我們在北極失去海冰時，北極熊將會挨餓」。</span></blockquote><br />\n可能咋，睇埋內文先覆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無埋到隻熊身<br />\n根本無人知隻熊係乜嘢事<br />\nChristina咁做係想用北極熊嚟引起大家關注冰川溶化嘅問題"},{"pid":"ace0b8379730abeb7a3798938bbb83f38d7c8336","tid":494378,"uid":126100,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:08:22.000Z","msg":"環保只係門生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76eefa8d607a308a245d4126f735a835c53f175f","tid":494378,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:10:58.000Z","msg":"我無下一代，關我叉事"},{"pid":"1fb938db19c17a5ccf51f98926b1366ad3cfe93a","tid":494378,"uid":33777,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:26:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔幫又要影人<br />\n拍野浪費資源又唔環保<br />\n<br />\n佢咁瘦又唔幫人渡過難關<br />\n環保撚真係黑心，得個講字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171209/57559505\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171209%2F57559505&d=I